msgstr "Par défaut : 0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:361
msgid "Units to use when defining the output raster size/resolution. One of:"
msgstr ""
"Unités à utiliser lors de la définition de la taille / résolution du raster "
"en sortie. Un des:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:364
msgid "0 --- Pixels"
msgstr "0 --- Pixels"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:365
msgid "1 --- Georeferenced units"
msgstr "1 --- Unités géoréférencées"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:367
msgid "**Width/Horizontal resolution**"
msgstr "**Largeur/résolution horizontale**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:368
msgid "``WIDTH``"
msgstr "``WIDTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:372
msgid ""
"Sets the width (if size units is \"Pixels\") or horizontal resolution (if "
"size units is \"Georeferenced units\") of the output raster. Minimum value: "
"0.0."
msgstr ""
"Définit la largeur (si les unités de taille sont des \"pixels\") ou la "
"résolution horizontale (si les unités de taille sont des \"unités "
"géoréférencées\") du raster en sortie. Valeur minimale: 0.0."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:375
msgid "**Height/Vertical resolution**"
msgstr "**Hauteur/résolution verticale**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:376
msgid "``HEIGHT``"
msgstr "``HEIGHT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:380
msgid ""
"Sets the height (if size units is \"Pixels\") or vertical resolution (if "
"size units is \"Georeferenced units\") of the output raster."
msgstr ""
"Définit la hauteur (si les unités de taille sont des \"pixels\") ou la "
"résolution verticale (si les unités de taille sont des \"unités "
"géoréférencées\") du raster en sortie."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:383
msgid "**Output extent**"
msgstr "**Étendue de sortie**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:386
msgid "``EXTENT``"
msgstr "``EXTENT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:387
msgid "[extent]"
msgstr "[emprise]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:388
msgid ""
"Extent of the output raster layer. If the extent is not specified, the "
"minimum extent that covers the selected reference layer(s) will be used."
msgstr ""
"Étendue de la couche raster en sortie. Si l'étendue n'est pas spécifiée, "
"l'étendue minimale qui couvre la ou les couches de référence sélectionnées "
"sera utilisée."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:3
msgid "Available methods are:"
msgstr "Les méthodes disponibles sont:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:5
msgid ""
"Calculate from layer…: uses extent of a layer loaded in the current project"
msgstr ""
"Calculer à partir d'une couche... : utilise l'étendue d'une couche chargée "
"dans le projet actuel"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:6
msgid ""
"Calculate from layout map…: uses extent of a :ref:`layout map item "
"<layout_map_item>` in the active project"
msgstr ""
"Calculer depuis une carte de mise en page... : utilise l'étendue d'un "
"élément :ref:`carte de mise en page <layout_map_item>` du projet actif"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:8
msgid ""
"Calculate from bookmark…: uses extent of a saved :ref:`bookmark "
"<sec_bookmarks>`"
msgstr ""
"Calculer depuis  un signet... : utilise l'étendue d'un :ref:`signet "
"géospatial <sec_bookmarks>` précédemment sauvegardé"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:9
msgid "Use map canvas extent"
msgstr "Utiliser l'emprise du canevas de la carte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:10
msgid ""
"Draw on canvas: click and drag a rectangle delimiting the area to take into "
"account"
msgstr ""
"Dessiner sur le canevas de carte : cliquer et dessiner un rectangle "
"délimitant la zone à prendre en compte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:11
msgid "Enter the coordinates as ``xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax``"
msgstr "Entrer les  coordonnées  ``xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:396
msgid "**Assign a specified NoData value to output bands**"
msgstr "**Attribuer une valeur NoData définie aux bandes de sortie**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:399
msgid "``NODATA``"
msgstr "``NODATA``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:408
msgid "Default: ``[Save to temporary file]``"
msgstr "Par défaut : ``[Enregistrer dans un fichier temporaire]``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:409
msgid ""
"Specification of the output raster layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr "Choix de la couche raster de sortie parmi une des options suivantes :"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:440
msgid ""
"For adding one or more creation options that control the raster to be "
"created (colors, block size, file compression...). For convenience, you can "
"rely on predefined profiles (see :ref:`GDAL driver options section "
"<gdal_createoptions>`)."
msgstr ""
"Pour ajouter une ou plusieurs options de création qui contrôlent le raster à"
" créer (couleurs, taille de bloc, compression de fichier ...). Pour plus de "
"commodité, vous pouvez utiliser des profils prédéfinis (voir les "
":ref:`options de pilote GDAL <gdal_createoptions>`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:446
msgid ""
"Batch Process and Model Designer: separate multiple options with a pipe "
"character (``|``)."
msgstr ""
"Pour le processus en lot et le modeleur graphique : séparez les différentes "
"options avec le caractère pipe (``|``)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:448
msgid "**Output data type**"
msgstr "**Type de données de sortie**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:449
msgid "``DATA_TYPE``"
msgstr "``DATA_TYPE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:452
msgid "Default: 5"
msgstr "Par défaut : 5 "

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:453
msgid "Defines the format of the output raster file."
msgstr "Définit le format du fichier raster en sortie."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectorconversion.rst:455
msgid "Options:"
msgstr "Options :"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:9
msgid "0 --- Byte        (Eight bit unsigned integer (quint8))"
msgstr "0 --- Byte        (Entier 8 bit non signé (quint8))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:10
msgid "1 --- Int16       (Sixteen bit signed integer (qint16))"
msgstr "1 --- Int16       (Entier 16 bit signé (qint16))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:11
msgid "2 --- UInt16      (Sixteen bit unsigned integer (quint16))"
msgstr "2 --- UInt16      (Entier 16 bit non signé (quint16))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:12
msgid "3 --- UInt32      (Thirty two bit unsigned integer (quint32))"
msgstr "3 --- UInt32      (Entier 32 bit non signé (quint32))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:13
msgid "4 --- Int32       (Thirty two bit signed integer (qint32))"
msgstr "4 --- Int32       (Entier 32 bit signé (qint32))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:14
msgid "5 --- Float32     (Thirty two bit floating point (float))"
msgstr "5 --- Float32     (Trente-deux bits à virgule flottante (float))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:15
msgid "6 --- Float64     (Sixty four bit floating point (double))"
msgstr "6 --- Float64     (Soixante-quatre bits à virgule flottante (double))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:16
msgid "7 --- CInt16      (Complex Int16)"
msgstr "7 --- CInt16      (Complexe Int16)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:17
msgid "8 --- CInt32      (Complex Int32)"
msgstr "8 --- CInt32      (Complexe Int32)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:18
msgid "9 --- CFloat32    (Complex Float32)"
msgstr "9 --- CFloat32   (Complexe Float32)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:19
msgid "10 --- CFloat64   (Complex Float64)"
msgstr "10 --- CFloat64   (Complexe Float64)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:20
msgid "11 --- Int8       (Eight bit signed integer (qint8))"
msgstr "11 --- Int8       (Entier 8 bit signé (qint8))"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:22
msgid ""
"Available options depend on the GDAL version built with QGIS (see "
":menuselection:`Help --> About` menu)"
msgstr ""
"Les options disponibles dépendent de la version de GDAL compilée avec votre "
"version de QGIS (voir le menu :menuselection:`Aide --> A propos`)"

